Common format // HL
% bazel (build | test | run) //path/to/package:target

Build everything in a workspace // HL
% bazel build //...
or
% bazel build //:all

Build everything in package "abc" recursively // HL
% bazel build //abc/...
or
% bazel build //abc/:all

Build external dependency // HL
% bazel build @hw_generator//...

Build one target // HL
% bazel build //go:hello-world

Run one target // HL
% bazel run //go:hello-world
